ind:hedisMeasureId rdf:type rdf:Property ;
    rdfs:label 'Hedis Measure Id' ;
    rdfs:comment 'Foreign key linking to care.hedis_measure. Business justification: gap.hedis_measure_code is a denormalized string reference to the HEDIS measure catalog. Care gaps are frequently defined by non-compliance with specific HEDIS measures (e.g., a gap for HbA1c testing m' ;
