    rdfs:comment 'Foreign key linking to provider.provider. Business justification: Risk adjustment and HCC coding workflows require knowing which provider diagnosed each condition. CMS risk adjustment audits and RADV reviews trace HCC codes to diagnosing providers. Role-prefix \'diag' ;
